---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Solana Breakpoint 2021 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Lisbon, Portugal</div>
        <div class="event-title">Solana<br />Breakpoint<br />2021</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Produced while the world was still shut down, and relying entirely on one site visit and the trust of our local partners, Solana Breakpoint saw over 2,000 attendees across 6 venues in Lisbon, just when borders were reopening.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>Production is what we're known for. Together with the amazing team at Europalco, we created custom projection and LED boards for all 3 main stage venues. Our talented designer pool made the stages come to life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Registration</div>
            <p>We gave out over 1,200 badges and swag bags the day before Breakpoint began. The excitement was palpable, and the decision to host a registration warm-up party the day before Breakpoint took a huge burden off of the registration teams on Day 1. Registration was held at all 4 venues after that.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">On-Site</div>
            <p>We're only as good as the team around us. We've cultivated important relationships in Lisbon over the years, and for Breakpoint 2021 we relied on the expertise of our trusted partners. We managed over 100 on-site temporary event staff, security teams, production teams, and transportation staff.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
